1.1
log
@Initial revision
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: print.c,v 1.9 2002/02/16 21:27:08 millert Exp $	*/
/*	$NetBSD: print.c,v 1.11 1996/05/07 18:20:10 jtc Exp $	*/

